&gt;Peterson was an old fox. He was short at only four feet tall and his once luscious tail now looked like a wilted flower due to age. Just as well, his orange fur had also dulled considerably over the years and he seemed to walk with a slight limp. You noticed one of his ears had also been torn and scarred over.
